name: Africa Petite Studs ...in silver mirror acrylic
description:
Simple, elegant and tres chic! These beauties measure .75" inches and in this case...size doesn't matter, they boldly hold their own with lots of shimmer and reflective shine. Made of silver acrylic mirror with surgical steel posts.

Very versatile and perfect worn alone or paired with an ear cuff, a long feather or chain earring...endless possibilities.

Perfect for a gift and comes beautifully boxed ready for gift giving.

name: Large African Continents
description: Simply Gorgeous! These earrings are 3" inches and are in silver acrylic mirror with silver hardware. They are large and lightweight with a bold and straightforward edge. I had a hard time capturing their true beauty with my camera....they are really quite stunning in person.

name: Ninth Dynasty .....earrings
description:
These artisan handcrafted stunning earrings are Egyptian inspired. Large faceted shimmering teal blue peacock colored crystals suspend open golden pyramids that have been handcrafted from brass sheet metal. Smaller pyramids sway in articulate movement from the center of each pyramid.

Comes ready for gift-giving

2.50 inches in length
2 inches in width
Gold plated ear wires
Very lightweight

name: Colorful Agate and Cowrie shell Charm Bracelet
description:
Beautiful pink, blue, green and black agate gemstones in the shape of sticks are wire wrapped onto large solid brass link chain. For that unexpected extra, we've added batik carved bone beads and cowrie shells for a little extra humph!

This bracelet adds a special and unique touch to any outfit!

Fit for any goddess.

Very earthy and natural.


measures 8.50 inches with a 1.50 extension chain
Can be shortened or extended upon request
Lobster claw closure
Comes ready to gift

name: Morrocan Honey Copal Amber ...X-large Cocktail Ring
description:
This ring has a real regal look, it is simplistic and yet bold and modern with an old world/ancient feel.

It features an earthy extra large copal amber stone that is the color of tupelo honey with a setting of brass that is ornate and has a lovely patina for a slightly aged look.

It has an adjustable band that is soldered (not glued) and sits poised and elegant on your hand.

The inside copal amber stone is a little over 1.25 inches in length by 1 inch wide.

Lightweight and Comfortable!

Complimentary gift wrap.
